  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Complete  Shea Butter Processing Centre-Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will complete  the development of a Shea butter processing for 200 rural women in Ntereso Community in the Bole district of the Savannah region of Ghana. The women would be able to increase their incomes by 60% through increased production of quality Shea butter for the market. They will gain skills through training in processing the butter produced into value-added products such as soap, pomade and hair-food for the beauty market.</narrative>
  </description>
